{"tid":500723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俾法拉利追撞尾 本來想落車屌佢 但...","createTime":"2017-12-16T05:34:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-16T06:30:13.000Z","uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c56b026d1ce87c24f3e1c05e3ae3592e6c4b4028","tid":500723,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T05:34:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171216/640_59841c67f49bf427273edff2e1202d51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171216%2F640_59841c67f49bf427273edff2e1202d51.jpg&h=5a4d4f6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網易》報導，這輛紅色法拉利先是追撞了一輛白色本田轎車，由於速度過快，導致本田車又往前追撞了另一輛車，造成連環追撞。而且本田車在法拉利的追撞下，後車箱整個變形，這原本讓本田的車主相當不爽，且法拉利車主遲遲不肯下車。直到警方獲報來現場處理，法拉利車主才下車，但她一下車，讓人眼睛為之一亮，現場的人皆紛紛認為她是「爆乳正妹」。而這位爆乳正妹在事發當時腳踩高跟鞋，可能是讓她無法順利控制剎車的原因。<br />\n據悉原本本田車主非常生氣，但在看到法拉利的正妹車主後，連重話都不好意思說。女車主也覺得不好意思，留了聯繫方式。另外報導指出，女車主駕駛的法拉利應是2015款California，售價約新台幣2500萬元，最高車速可達316km/h，最大馬力560匹。"},{"pid":"7969ab9f1a4e952911940a7a09e9a0c0f88ba3c7","tid":500723,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T05:37:30.000Z","msg":"唔想屌係咩諗法?"},{"pid":"c5bac9685ad3b7f76b34d03a9a403a6a016a9ed2","tid":500723,"uid":31219,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T05:38:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">女車主也覺得不好意思，留了聯繫方式。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"329e57da4465db504a8c7799a6d6878413160e07","tid":500723,"uid":22624,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T05:38:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔想屌係咩諗法?</blockquote><br />\n唔想屌，因為想屌"},{"pid":"e1fde7cec39bb316f2854f5c8a5c8ff30660c5ef","tid":500723,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T05:38:44.000Z","msg":"雞"},{"pid":"bb0ff0d09e09cbf257c84c9372f1e65a57dbb081","tid":500723,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T05:39:59.000Z","msg":"台灣好多偽娘可能有j都唔定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"565e2756b1be22cfb0ae6560e178601a8296eb79","tid":500723,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T05:42:54.000Z","msg":"其實個樣好醜"},{"pid":"5dddec607b5d66445f5c3b57d6dc95a1dafbe2c0","tid":500723,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T05:43:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d78d44eae910f3e3c9e028a6ac635f7f09c9a2e","tid":500723,"uid":48817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T05:53:40.000Z","msg":"咁有錢都要著到成隻雞咁，定係原本就係雞搭上有錢佬。"},{"pid":"062c9f67c3664be405ae18a40bc60f6554059f02","tid":500723,"uid":2854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T05:55:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁有錢都要著到成隻雞咁，定係原本就係雞搭上有錢佬。</blockquote><br />\n後者"},{"pid":"4b33c2c3a6845f7f5506d7b3bc57cb8a5950f982","tid":500723,"uid":152726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T06:13:23.000Z","msg":"屌唔係得個講字，要做"},{"pid":"7257be361b514e6e03fb780cf006b1d294c853e7","tid":500723,"uid":49918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T06:14:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"60065d121b6eb759f0056741e0c6934f47662b09","tid":500723,"uid":87600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T06:15:03.000Z","msg":"男人黎"},{"pid":"cbaa9c9a377492a0c9c683c65886d0f3e06c1c83","tid":500723,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T06:30:13.000Z","msg":"醜人多百怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}